commit message: Fix handling of null values for Strings in payment protocol.
Fix broken check of payment request expiry time.
More logging when fetching and parsing external data.
Catch crash when loader execution is rejected.
Send user agent with all HTTP requests.
Fix background color of forms in dialogs for Gingerbread.
Fix background color of dialog titles on Gingerbread.
Undo workaround for fetching the name of the CA that verified the payment request.
Remove check for payment message equality when parsing payment ack. Somehow it triggers a bug in the generated protobuf code.
